  "response": "```dockerfile
# Stage 1: chef
FROM rust:1.78 AS chef
WORKDIR /app
RUN cargo install cargo-chef
COPY . .
RUN cargo chef prepare --recipe-path recipe.json

# Stage 2: rust-builder
FROM rust:1.78 AS rust-builder
WORKDIR /app
COPY --from=chef /app/recipe.json recipe.json
RUN cargo chef cook --release --recipe-path recipe.json
COPY . .
RUN cargo build --release

# Stage 3: python-builder
FROM python:3.11-slim AS python-builder
WORKDIR /app
ENV PATH="/opt/venv/bin:$PATH"
RUN python -m venv /opt/venv && \
    pip install --no-cache-dir --extra-index-url https://download.pytorch.org/whl/cpu torch transformers tokenizers safetensors

# Stage 4: runtime
FROM debian:bookworm-slim AS runtime

LABEL maintainer="ml-team@example.com" \
      org.opencontainers.image.source="https://github.com/org/repo" \
      org.opencontainers.image.description="Rust + Python ML Inference Server"

RUN apt-get update && \
    apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends curl python3 libpython3.11 && \
    rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/* && \
    addgroup --system --gid 1000 inference && \
    adduser --system --uid 1000 --ingroup inference inference

WORKDIR /app

COPY --from=python-builder --chown=1000:1000 /opt/venv /opt/venv
ENV PATH="/opt/venv/bin:$PATH"

COPY --from=rust-builder --chown=1000:1000 /app/target/release/inference-server /usr/local/bin/inference-server

USER inference

EXPOSE 8080

HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=3s --start-period=5s --retries=3 \
    CMD curl -f http://localhost:8080/health || exit 1

CMD ["/usr/local/bin/inference-server", "--port", "8080"]
